Render directory tree and file contents from a Git repository

Usage: codicat [OPTIONS] [PATH]

Arguments:
  [PATH]  Path to render (defaults to current directory) [default: .]

Options:
      --max-lines <MAX_LINES>  Limit the number of lines printed per file [default: 500]
      --no-tree                Do not render the tree view
      --no-content             Do not render file contents
      --copy                   Copy output to clipboard
      --fzf                    Interactively select files via fzf (if installed)
      --filter <FILTER>        Filter file paths with a regular expression
  -h, --help                   Print help
  -V, --version                Print version
